.Nd
usernland Lustre networking routing daemon runtime control
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm lnrtctl
.Op Fl HI
.Op Fl p Ar paramspec
.Op Fl S Ar socket
.Op Fl s Ar showspec
.Op Ar cmd arg ...
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
utility controls
.Xr lnrtd 8
behavior.
.Pp
